                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5577" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">STR-1414</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8909 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">更上一层楼：华新水泥十四五期间如何实现业绩倍增？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Ascending to a Higher Level：How Can Huaxin Cement Double Its Performance During the 14th Five Year Plan Period</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">田志龙，杨玲，李叶青，江涛，叶济群</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华中科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华新水泥股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">建筑、建材业与房地产业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规划计划部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">24 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略规划； 战略决策；战略宣贯；华新水泥；2021百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strategic Planning；Strategic Decision；Publicity and Implementation of the Strategy；Huaxin Cement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略规划是企业的重要战略管理工作之一。通过系统制定公司的发展目标、战略思路以及具体举措，战略规划能够助力企业长期生存和发展。本案例首先介绍了水泥行业的百年上市公司华新水泥的发展概况、行业背景，然后回顾了华新水泥制定“业绩倍增计划”（即“十四五”规划）的战略规划过程。通过描绘这一过程，本案例旨在促进学生了解企业内部进行战略规划的步骤、要点、参与的部门与人员等；同时引导学生通过使用战略分析与战略决策工具，理解企业制定中长期战略目标、提出战略思路的依据，以及三层战略之间的关联与衔接。本案例可用于《战略管理》课程的战略规划、战略决策等内容的教学。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Strategic planning is an important part of enterprise strategic management. Through the systematic formulation of the company&#39;s objectives, strategic ideas and specific measures, strategic planning helps the long-term survival and development of enterprises. First, this case introduces the development situation of Huaxin Cement and the background of Cement industry，which is a century old listed company in the cement industry. Then this case reviews the strategic planning process of Huaxin Cement in formulating the &quot;performance doubling plan&quot; (the 14th five year plan). By describing this process, this case aims to promote students to understand the steps, key points, departments and personnel involved in the strategic planning within the enterprise. In addition, this case aims to guide students to understand the basis for enterprises to formulate medium and long-term strategic objectives and strategic ideas, as well as the connection and cohesion between the three levels of strategy through the use of strategic analysis and strategic decision-making tools. This case can be used in the course of strategic management，especially in the teaching of strategic planning and strategic decision.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略规划与战略决策过程</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-10</td>
                            </tr>
